                                        b Hi <?=$variable?>!
                                    br
                                    p Welcome on board of Kibu Hackathon 2015!
                                    br/
                                    p
                                        | We got your registration. You are in!
                                        | You can find all the essential
                                        | information about the event&nbsp;
