                                                | here
                                        |.
                                    br/
                                    p
                                        | If you have any additional questions
                                        | or for some reasons you&lsquo;ll be
                                        | unable to attend, please let us know
                                        | by sending us an&nbsp;
                                        a(href   = 'mailto:hello@kitchenbudapest.hu?' +
                                                   'subject=Kibu+Hackathon+2015'
                                          target = '_blank')
                                              font(color = colors.orange)
                                                  | email
                                        |.
                                    br/
                                    p
                                        | Looking forward to seeing you on 2
                                        sup nd
                                        | October at 6:00 PM!
                                    br/
                                    p
                                        i Cheers,
                                    br/
                                    p
                                        b Kibu Hackathon Team
